Build a REST API with Django

REST framework requires the following:
	PyCharm (or any other Editor)
	Python (2.7, 3.2, 3.3, 3.4, 3.5)
	Django (1.7+, 1.8, 1.9, 1.10) ==> pip install django==1.8
	Django Rest Framework ==> pip install djangorestframework

Steps:

	create project
	$ django-admin startproject TaskAPI

	create App
	$ python manage.py startapp TaskApp

	1. Create Task Model
	2. Create Task Serializer
	3. Create View
	4. Create Url Patterns
	5. Test REST API
